N.B. Own script option 35 characters only
Please either put details on paypal payment or email us direct on contact@healthful.uk.com

name: Canine Behaviour Consult in your own home
description:
If you are having behaviour issues with your dog or dogs, I can help. Consults may take between 2-4 hours and are designed to teach you how to effectively communicate with your pets in order to attain greater understanding and a more symbiotic relationship.

N.B. Price excludes travel at 40p per mile after the first 10 miles

name: Nutrition Consulation (Phone)
description:
Nutrition Consultation over the phone.

Details of all issues including behaviours and diet will be needed to be provided.

If we cannot make any suggestion immediately, we will do some research and come back to you as soon as possible.

N.B. We do not diagnose or prescribe, but can suggest foods or herbs that have been shown to help.
